13:09.092 --> 13:10.877
COME ON, GO, GO, GO!

13:11.007 --> 13:14.706
COME ON, LANI! LET'S GO, GO!

13:17.231 --> 13:18.493
-YES!

13:19.320 --> 13:22.540
-[CHEERING]

