-MITCH: WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, HEY. THAT'S ENOUGH.

13:44.084 --> 13:45.041
KNOCK IT OFF!

13:45.172 --> 13:46.651
-HE WAS ALL OVER ME OUT THERE!

13:46.782 --> 13:49.002
HE SHOULD BE DISQUALIFIED,
WHAT ARE YOU BLIND?

13:49.132 --> 13:50.220
-I WAS WATCHING,
IF ANYBODY SHOULD

13:50.351 --> 13:51.439
BE DISQUALIFIED IT'S YOU.

13:51.569 --> 13:53.093
-MITCH: HANG ON, HANG ON.

13:53.223 --> 13:55.443
THESE GUYS ARE ON
REPORT. KNOCK IT OFF!

13:56.966 --> 13:59.099
-COME ON, UP TO
HEADQUARTERS, BOTH OF YOU.

13:59.229 --> 14:02.189
-HEY, HEY, HEY. YOU
GONNA BE ALL RIGHT?

14:02.754 --> 14:04.147
YOU GOT NOTHING
TO BE ASHAMED OF,

14:04.278 --> 14:06.062
YOU GAVE IT YOUR
BEST SHOT OUT THERE.

14:06.802 --> 14:09.587
-THANKS FOR LETTING ME TRY
OUT, LIEUTENANT BUCHANNON.

14:10.066 --> 14:13.374
HAVE A GREAT SUMMER, I'M
SORRY I WON'T BE A PART OF IT.

14:15.985 --> 14:20.990
-[SOFT MUSIC]

14:21.861 --> 14:24.298
-HEY, CHERYL, GREAT
SWIM. CONGRATULATIONS.

14:24.428 --> 14:26.517
-THANKS, THANKS, THANKS A LOT.

14:26.909 --> 14:28.084
THANKS FOR THE OINTMENT.

14:28.215 --> 14:29.738
IT'S SO COLD OUT THERE.

14:29.869 --> 14:30.782
-CONGRATULATIONS.

14:30.913 --> 14:32.045
-THANK YOU.

14:32.175 --> 14:33.133
-GOOD SWIM, LADIES.

14:33.263 --> 14:34.438
-THANKS.

14:34.569 --> 14:36.440
-9:30 TONIGHT,
THAT'S SET IN STONE?

14:36.571 --> 14:38.268
