15:10.822 --> 15:13.303
-ARE YOU KIDDING?
I REALLY MADE IT?

15:13.434 --> 15:14.217
-ALL RIGHT, APRIL!

15:14.348 --> 15:15.566
-THANK YOU SO MUCH.

15:15.697 --> 15:17.568
-HEY, HEY, HEY, WAIT A MINUTE.

15:17.699 --> 15:19.092
