15:19.222 --> 15:20.310
-YEAH, I KNOW.

15:20.441 --> 15:21.703
-SO HOW COME I
DON'T GET THE SPOT?

15:21.833 --> 15:23.705
-IT'S NOT ALL ABOUT
PHYSICAL ABILITY.

15:23.835 --> 15:25.315
-YEAH, I GUESS IT'S
WHO'S THE BIGGEST SUCK UP,

15:25.446 --> 15:26.664
THAT'S HOW YOU
GET TO BE A LIFEGUARD.

15:26.795 --> 15:28.492
-NO, IT'S ABOUT
WHO WE CAN COUNT ON.

15:28.623 --> 15:30.930
-YEAH, WELL, GOOD LUCK IF
YOU'RE GONNA COUNT ON HER, PAL.

15:33.628 --> 15:34.977
-GIRL: WHAT A JERK.

15:36.413 --> 15:37.762
-CONGRATULATIONS.

15:38.241 --> 15:39.547
-THANKS.

